                                        boolean includeValues,

                                        boolean recursive,
                                        boolean caseSensitive,
                                        java.util.regex.Pattern pattern)
        Return a list of objects in the model that match the specified search.
        Parameters:
        container - The container within which to search.
        text - The text to find.
        includeValues - True to search values of Settable objects.
        includeNames - True to include names of objects.
        recursive - True to search within objects immediately contained.
        caseSensitive - True to match the case.
        pattern - The text compiled as a pattern, or null if the text could not be compiled as a pattern.
        Returns:
        The list of objects in the model that match the specified search.
